stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Discovered: manifest indexed
  Discovered --> Downloaded: user installs plugin
  Downloaded --> Verified: hash/signature check
  Verified --> Loaded: instantiate WASM component
  Loaded --> Setup: setup() called
  Setup --> Running: permissions granted
  Setup --> Blocked: permission denied
  Blocked --> Uninstalled: user removes plugin

  Running --> Ingesting: ingest() scheduled
  Ingesting --> Normalizing: plugin emits raw payload
  Normalizing --> Persisting: kernel normalises to JSON-LD
  Persisting --> Running: node stored via storage adapter

  Running --> Metadata: metadata() requested
  Metadata --> Running

  Running --> Teardown: disable or shutdown
  Teardown --> Loaded

  Loaded --> Uninstalled: uninstall command
  Uninstalled --> [*]
